<!-- Slide 11: Operations Switch-Out -->
<div class="slide-container" id="slide11">
    <h2 class="slide-title">
        <span lang="en">V. Operational: Switch-Out Mechanism</span>
        <span lang="id">V. Operasional: Mekanisme Switch-Out</span>
    </h2>
    <div class="content-area">
        <div class="two-column" style="gap: 40px; align-items: center;">
            <!-- Definition -->
            <div>
                <h3 style="color: #d97706;">
                    <span lang="en">Inactive Participant Policy</span>
                    <span lang="id">Kebijakan Peserta Tidak Aktif</span>
                </h3>
                <p style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
                    <span lang="en">To ensure flexibility and maintain a stable number of active seats, we apply a "Seat Model" where the insurer keeps the seat, but the participant occupying it can be replaced.</span>
                    <span lang="id">Untuk menjaga fleksibilitas dan kestabilan jumlah seat aktif, kami menerapkan "Model Seat" di mana asuransi memiliki kursi, namun peserta yang mengisinya dapat diganti.</span>
                </p>
                <div class="tile centered" style="background-color: #fff7ed; border-color: #d97706;">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-user-slash" style="font-size: 40px; color: #d97706; margin-bottom: 15px;"></i>
                    <h4 style="margin: 0; color: #9a3412; font-size: 18px;">
                        <span lang="en">"Inactive" Definition</span>
                        <span lang="id">Definisi "Tidak Aktif"</span>
                    </h4>
                    <p style="font-size: 16px; margin-top: 5px;">
                        <span lang="en">30 consecutive days of zero logging/activity and no coaching interaction.</span>
                        <span lang="id">30 hari berturut-turut tanpa logging/aktivitas dan tanpa interaksi coaching.</span>
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Mechanics -->
            <div class="tile" style="background-color: #F8FAFC; border-left: 4px solid #d97706;">
                <div class="bullet-list">
                    <ul>
                        <li>
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-rotate"></i>
                            <strong><span lang="en">Frequency:</span><span lang="id">Frekuensi:</span></strong>
                            <br>
                            <span lang="en">MNC Life may request a Switch-Out <strong>once per annum per participant slot</strong>.</span>
                            <span lang="id">MNC Life dapat melakukan Switch-Out <strong>1 kali per tahun per seat</strong>.</span>
                        </li>
                        <li style="margin-top: 25px;">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-file-invoice-dollar"></i>
                            <strong><span lang="en">Billing Effect:</span><span lang="id">Efek Billing:</span></strong>
                            <br>
                            <span lang="en">Billing for the Inactive Participant stops starting from the <strong>next Billing Cycle (21st)</strong> after Switch-Out confirmation.</span>
                            <span lang="id">Penagihan peserta tidak aktif berhenti mulai <strong>Billing Cycle berikutnya (tgl 21)</strong> setelah konfirmasi.</span>
                        </li>
                        <li style="margin-top: 25px;">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-user-plus"></i>
                            <strong><span lang="en">Replacement:</span><span lang="id">Penggantian:</span></strong>
                            <br>
                            <span lang="en">Billing for the replacement begins only after successful Onboarding.</span>
                            <span lang="id">Penagihan peserta pengganti dimulai hanya setelah Onboarding berhasil.</span>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

